The arithmetic confirms three structural facts:

**Fact 1.** The ring's spectral radius ρ = 1+√3 is an algebraic integer in Z[√3], the ring of integers of Q(√3). Its minimal polynomial x²−2x−2 has discriminant 12, the discriminant of Q(√3).

